{"tid":2095564,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想為自己而生存","createTime":"2020-07-05T14:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T17:02:41.000Z","uid":251499,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"23c0a4ba533dae4042db04877df33a5030b2fa96","tid":2095564,"uid":251499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:15:59.000Z","msg":"唔想再為生存而生存，唔想再為生存而消耗時間，唔想再為生存而消磨意志。<br />\n<br />\n我剩係想每日有時間望下藍天白雲，每日可以訓夠覺先起身，每日都做到屬於我興趣嘅嘢。<br />\n我不過想平凡過一生，但原來己經係屬於夢幻般嘅追求，係少數人先擁有到嘅生活。<br />\n<br />\n我已經好攰，攰到覺得生存開始變得模糊，模糊到看不清。"},{"pid":"89475241f4b93c563a223212631b6bd292a2a881","tid":2095564,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"ifc is waiting for you"},{"pid":"351ded9411957760d409569c3c713d5b8b1d5add","tid":2095564,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"樓主讀書定做野"},{"pid":"6e2ece478e292ab619f788a7a2941f74a22a2336","tid":2095564,"uid":129436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"休息吓吧"},{"pid":"33bd82175158beb6b8b8e3163d22e4486403639f","tid":2095564,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"讀緊書定做緊野？"},{"pid":"c6f6673db2780e0daa4dd1448ab4ea4e6886d741","tid":2095564,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T14:46:44.000Z","msg":"我好接近了<br />\n如果我可以殺一個我好撚憎人會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5051985f2b843f9b32eddcb1fcabd578a6e35c1a","tid":2095564,"uid":275818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"同感 日日為咗生活而生活 唔知自己做緊咩"},{"pid":"d34abeb3142ca3822047bdfee7b1a37481b3cf11","tid":2095564,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T17:02:41.000Z","msg":"fighting ٩(˃̶͈̀௰˂̶͈́)و"}]}